/status/1196133437251506178?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1196133437251506178%3Fs%3D20&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=5008d55e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1196133437251506178%3Fs%3D20&h=c994d01d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1196133437251506178?s=20</a><br />\n眾志<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196112617892220928?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196112617892220928%3Fs%3D21&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=24031685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196112617892220928%3Fs%3D21&h=bd4340c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196112617892220928?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察暴行<br />\n克警用示威者頭部撞擊石屎地<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkdnow1/status/1196316374781419520?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkdnow1%2Fstatus%2F1196316374781419520%3Fs%3D21&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=dd76f588\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkdnow1%2Fstatus%2F1196316374781419520%3Fs%3D21&h=e2b5b9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkdnow1/status/1196316374781419520?s=21</a><br />\n眾志講警察拖示威者之後再兜頭踩<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196392281432977408?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196392281432977408%3Fs%3D21&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=f7ab9906\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fstatus%2F1196392281432977408%3Fs%3D21&h=ff015117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1196392281432977408?s=21</a><br />\n克警踢頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196193334194319367?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196193334194319367%3Fs%3D21&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=a0e33771\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196193334194319367%3Fs%3D21&h=79bf8464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196193334194319367?s=21</a><br />\n講警察當醫生護士fa係犯人,全部反鎖雙手<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1196107736779354114?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1196107736779354114%3Fs%3D20&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=af16294b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1196107736779354114%3Fs%3D20&h=723549c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1196107736779354114?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196107058136961025?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196107058136961025%3Fs%3D21&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=5bad6ba9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1196107058136961025%3Fs%3D21&h=a023b2b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1196107058136961025?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n人權法案情況<br />\n美國參議院啟動「熱線」機制推進參議院版本的《香港人權與民主法案》（下稱香港人權法）。倘獲參議院通過，參眾兩院其後需要啟動「和解程序」，將兩個版本香港人權法合二為一，交由總統特朗普（Donald Trump）簽署生效。不過，特朗普其實可以動用「總統否決權」（Presidential Vetoes），令香港人權法不會生效。而在此情況下，國會亦有權推翻特朗普的對香港人權法的否決。<br />\n倘香港人權法獲通過，特朗普有甚麼選項？<br />\n（1）特朗普可在10日內（除周日以外）簽署協議，令香港人權法生效；<br />\n<br />\n（2）特朗普可不簽署法案，並在10日內（除周日以外）撰寫異議書（a statement of objections），再交回國會重審；<br />\n<br />\n（3）特朗普可選擇甚麼都不做，若該時並非國會的休會期，法案會在10日後就自動生效；<br />\n<br />\n（4）若香港人權法送達特朗普後，國會在10日內（除周日以外）休會，而特朗普選擇甚麼都不做，此法案會自動失效，這被稱為「口袋否決」（pocket veto）。<br />\n<br />\n若特朗普拒絕簽署，國會可怎樣？<br />\n國會可動議推翻特朗普的否決，倘在參眾兩院都獲得3分2的票數支持，就能推翻特朗普的否決權。特朗普必須接受國會的決定。"},{"pid":"9aeb803d8a432038b46dcb6e67a2d5cb67bf3a1b","tid":1735330,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}